---
// Problem section — Clean side-by-side comparison
---

<section id="problem" class="relative py-24 sm:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden">
  <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-[1400px] px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-10">
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-8 items-center">

      <!-- LEFT: The Problem (5 cols) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8">
        <div class="reveal">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-red-50 text-red-600 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v2m0 4h.01m-6.938 4h13.856c1.54 0 2.502-1.667 1.732-3L13.732 4c-.77-1.333-2.694-1.333-3.464 0L3.34 16c-.77 1.333.192 3 1.732 3z" /></svg>
            El Problema
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-slate-900 leading-tight">
            Buscar talento local es un <span class="text-red-500">caos</span>.
          </h2>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-1 flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-colors hover:border-red-200">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-red-600">📢</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Ofertas invisibles</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Las vacantes se pierden en grupos de WhatsApp saturados o postes en la calle. No hay centralización.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2 flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-colors hover:border-red-200">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-red-600">🔍</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Talento oculto</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Albañiles, electricistas y técnicos independientes no tienen un escaparate digital para ofrecer sus servicios.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex items-start gap-4 p-5 rounded-2xl bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 transition-colors hover:border-red-200">
            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 text-red-600">📋</div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-slate-900 mb-1">Cero seguimiento</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Cientos de hojas de vida en físico que se acumulan sin un proceso de selección organizado.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- CENTER: Connector -->
      <div class="hidden lg:flex lg:col-span-2 justify-center">
        <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-white shadow-soft border border-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center text-slate-400 z-10">
          <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3" /></svg>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- RIGHT: The Solution (5 cols) -->
      <div class="lg:col-span-5 space-y-8 p-8 sm:p-10 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-brand-900/20">
        <!-- Decoration -->
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-64 h-64 bg-brand-500/20 rounded-full blur-[80px]"></div>

        <div class="reveal relative z-10">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" /></svg>
            La Solución
          </span>
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-extrabold text-white leading-tight">
            LocalWork lo <span class="text-brand-400">conecta todo</span>.
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-4 text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">
            Una plataforma unificada con herramientas de clase mundial para potenciar la fuerza laboral de nuestra ciudad.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 reveal reveal-delay-1 relative z-10">
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">⚡</div>
            <p class="font-medium text-white text-sm mb-1">Postulación</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">A 1 solo clic</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">🔔</div>
            <p class="font-medium text-white text-sm mb-1">Alertas</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">En tiempo real</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">📊</div>
            <p class="font-medium text-white text-sm mb-1">Gestión</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Pipeline visual</p>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 rounded-2xl bg-white/5 border border-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm">
            <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-brand-500/20 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center mb-3">⭐</div>
            <p class="font-medium text-white text-sm mb-1">Reputación</p>
            <p class="text-xs text-slate-400">Calificaciones</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
